This is the repository for the Open Advice book. You can find the LaTeX source of the book here.
To build a pdf file out of the LaTeX source install LaTeX and run "pdflatex Open-Advice".

On Debian-based systems, you can install "pdflatex" with:

    sudo apt-get install texlive-latex-extra

The book and its content is licenced under CC-BY-SA. For questions about the
book contact Lydia Pintscher at lydia@kde.org.
